data.description: A lovely newer built (2022) farmhouse-style rambler with 5 Bedrooms along with an exercise room on the lower level. Very private property sitting on 6 acres.  Wide open floor space with high ceiling and beams in the living room, fireplace for cozy warm evenings, and very spacious bedrooms. Sellers sadly are moving due to job and family. No disappointment. Approx 2800  sq ft of living space. Presenting offers as they come in.
